lakshyam ( english : target ) is a 2007 telugu film produced by nallamalupu srinivas ( bujji ) on sri lakshmi narasimha productions banner and directed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . starring gopichand , jagapati babu , anushka in lead roles and music composed by mani sharma . the film recorded as super hit at box office . it was later remade in tamil as &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; velu , in bengali as fighter and in kannada as &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the movie was dubbed in hindi as bhai - the lion and in malayalam as chandu - the hot her .